Add ability to add source to charts In order for a charts/viz to be taken serious, it must have the source of the data attributed. This PR add ability to define source either as a link via `data-source` attribute on chart div (html) or as a `source` object in the `metadata` section of chart data (python). The second method also offer ability to separate the link and display title i.e. ``` html
``` ``` python data['metadata']['source'] = { 'title': 'Source Title', 'link': 'https://link', } ```
